             View your contacts as a table.  
             When in table-view mode, this menu item reads 
             <guimenuitem>As Minicards</guimenuitem>, and changes the view
             back to the minicard format.
           </para></listitem>
	  </varlistentry>	  
	</variablelist>      
      </para>
